HEADWORD: Kid
<hw>Kid</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. W. <ets>cidysen</ets>.]</ety>
<def>A fagot; a bundle of heath and furze.</def> <mark>[Prov.
Eng.]</mark> <rj><au>Wright.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Kid</ent>⟦br⟧

